Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:11.69,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I want to shine on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:15.03,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And always light the dazzling sun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:18.52,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I want to defend you from all the darkness
